{"name": "fjaraskupan", "metadata": {"name": "fjaraskupan", "version": "2.3.1", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Environment :: Console", "Framework :: AsyncIO", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License"], "home_page": "https://github.com/elupus/fjaraskupan", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["bleak"], "summary": "A python library for speaking to fj\u00e4r\u00e5skupan", "upload_time": 1734532389}, "documentation": ["# Fj\u00e4r\u00e5skupan Bluetooth Control\n\nThis module support controlling Fj\u00e4r\u00e5skupan kitchen fans over bluetooth\n\n## Status\n\n```{image} https://github.com/elupus/fjaraskupan/actions/workflows/python-package.yml/badge.svg\n:target: https://github.com/elupus/fjaraskupan\n```\n\n### Module\n\nCode to set fan speed using library.\n\n```python\nasync def run():\n    async with Device(\"AAAAAAAA-BBBB-CCCC-DDDD-EEEEEEEEEEEE\") as device:\n        await device.set_fan_speed(5)\n\nloop = asyncio.get_event_loop()\nloop.run_until_complete (run())\n```\n\n### Commandline\n\nScan for possible devices.\n\n```bash\npython -m fjaraskupan scan\n```\n\nCode to set fan speed using commandline.\n\n```bash\npython -m fjaraskupan fan AAAAAAAA-BBBB-CCCC-DDDD-EEEEEEEEEEEE 5\n```\n\nTo get help on possible commands\n\n```bash\npython -m fjaraskupan -h\npython -m fjaraskupan light -h\npython -m fjaraskupan fan -h\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "fjaraskupan.__main__", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "fjaraskupan.__main__.async_scan", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "args", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fjaraskupan.__main__.async_light", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "args", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fjaraskupan.__main__.async_fan", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "args", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fjaraskupan.__main